    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Title], [p].[Price], [p].[Description], [p].[Image], [p].[IsDelete], [p].[CreateDate], [p].[Slug]

) AS [t]

2024-12-28 14:09:00.2669|INFO|Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command|Executed DbCommand (76ms) [Parameters=[@__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[CategoryId], [t].[Title], [t].[Price], [t].[Description], [t].[Image], [t].[IsDelete], [t].[CreateDate], [t].[Slug], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Color], [t0].[ColorTitle], [t0].[CreateDate], [t0].[IsDelete], [t0].[Price], [t0].[ProductId], [t0].[Quantity], [p1].[Id], [p1].[CreateDate], [p1].[ProductId], [p1].[UserId], [p1].[Visit], [p2].[Id], [p2].[CreateDate], [p2].[ProductId], [p2].[Reaction], [p2].[UserId]
FROM (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Title], [p].[Price], [p].[Description], [p].[Image], [p].[IsDelete], [p].[CreateDate], [p].[Slug]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    WHERE [p].[IsDelete] = CAST(0 AS bit)
    ORDER BY [p].[CreateDate] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p0].[Id], [p0].[Color], [p0].[ColorTitle], [p0].[CreateDate], [p0].[IsDelete], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductId], [p0].[Quantity]
    FROM [ProductColors] AS [p0]
    WHERE [p0].[IsDelete] = CAST(0 AS bit)
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductVisits] AS [p1] ON [t].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductReactions] AS [p2] ON [t].[Id] = [p2].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [t].[CreateDate] DESC, [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [p1].[Id]

) AS [t]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductId]

    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [p].[Id], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreateDate], [p].[Description], [p].[GuarrantyText], [p].[Image], [p].[InfoDescription], [p].[IsDelete], [p].[IsFreeShipping], [p].[Price], [p].[Quantity], [p].[Review], [p].[Slug], [p].[Title], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [p0].[Visit]
        FROM [ProductVisits] AS [p0]
        WHERE [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]) AS [c]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY (
        SELECT TOP(1) [p0].[Visit]
        FROM [ProductVisits] AS [p0]
        WHERE [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]) DESC
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [ProductVisits] AS [p1] ON [t].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductReactions] AS [p2] ON [t].[Id] = [p2].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [t].[c] DESC, [t].[Id], [p1].[Id]

    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [p].[Id], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreateDate], [p].[Description], [p].[GuarrantyText], [p].[Image], [p].[InfoDescription], [p].[IsDelete], [p].[IsFreeShipping], [p].[Price], [p].[Quantity], [p].[Review], [p].[Slug], [p].[Title], (
        SELECT TOP(1) [p0].[Visit]
        FROM [ProductVisits] AS [p0]
        WHERE [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]) AS [c]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY (
        SELECT TOP(1) [p0].[Visit]
        FROM [ProductVisits] AS [p0]
        WHERE [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]) DESC
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [ProductVisits] AS [p1] ON [t].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductReactions] AS [p2] ON [t].[Id] = [p2].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [t].[c] DESC, [t].[Id], [p1].[Id]

    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
    LEFT JOIN [ProductColors] AS [p0] ON [o0].[ProductColorId] = [p0].[Id]
    WHERE [o0].[IsDelete] = CAST(0 AS bit)
) AS [t] ON [o].[Id] = [t].[OrderId]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[CategoryId], [t].[Title], [t].[Price], [t].[Description], [t].[Image], [t].[IsDelete], [t].[CreateDate], [t].[Slug], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Color], [t0].[ColorTitle], [t0].[CreateDate], [t0].[IsDelete], [t0].[Price], [t0].[ProductId], [t0].[Quantity], [p1].[Id], [p1].[CreateDate], [p1].[ProductId], [p1].[UserId], [p1].[Visit], [p2].[Id], [p2].[CreateDate], [p2].[ProductId], [p2].[Reaction], [p2].[UserId]
FROM (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Title], [p].[Price], [p].[Description], [p].[Image], [p].[IsDelete], [p].[CreateDate], [p].[Slug]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    WHERE [p].[IsDelete] = CAST(0 AS bit)
    ORDER BY [p].[CreateDate] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p0].[Id], [p0].[Color], [p0].[ColorTitle], [p0].[CreateDate], [p0].[IsDelete], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductId], [p0].[Quantity]
    FROM [ProductColors] AS [p0]
    WHERE [p0].[IsDelete] = CAST(0 AS bit)
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductVisits] AS [p1] ON [t].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductReactions] AS [p2] ON [t].[Id] = [p2].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [t].[CreateDate] DESC, [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [p1].[Id]

WHERE [o].[OrderId] = @__order_Id_0 AND [o].[IsDelete] = CAST(0 AS bit)
ORDER BY [o].[Id], [p].[Id]
